description: Refresh yourself the healthy way with Smoothie on Wheels’ delicious selection of premium real-fruit smoothies! With a registered dietitian behind the wheel of this tiki-bar truck, there are no artificial flavors or preservatives to be found here! Just delectable freshness. Ask anyone in Saratoga Springs and they’ll tell you that a sip of this fruity goodness is certainly worth a trip to Smoothies on Wheels.
name: Smoothies on Wheels
